sets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你又唔諗下自己咩身份<br />\n邊個莊邊個閒都未分清楚啦人地當你係雞黎炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靠得屋企玩車代表人地既價值同你唔同囉<br />\n你睇到舊錢咁大人地當散紙炸傻西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到人地好撚想娶你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有咁有志氣就啦啦聲分手搵個靠自己既男人啦垃圾"},{"pid":"01d68b7d27be37cb6cfc9cf0401ee0e0a67acad6","tid":650541,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08a3a77566e2ffe1bccfefe3d6bd00aaf0c364b8","tid":650541,"uid":50032,"like":119,"dislike":8,"score":111,"quote":{"pid":"d29bf4b8289aaa4fa6c9a42afc676f9d4ceda3df","tid":650541,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"錢真係咁重要？<br />\n車？樓？<br />\n依家d人真係咁現實？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:27:54.000Z","msg":"唔現實就假<br />\n我可以同你一齊儲首期，但結婚一定要有樓搬出黎住<br />\n車好少事，二手都係幾萬蚊<br />\n我唔介意你窮，但介意你花費起無謂嘢上面"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"有樓仲算唔算窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ea7b3f2ef5318e89e8a040db796f621f6d0302","tid":650541,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08a3a77566e2ffe1bccfefe3d6bd00aaf0c364b8","tid":650541,"uid":50032,"like":119,"dislike":8,"score":111,"quote":{"pid":"d29bf4b8289aaa4fa6c9a42afc676f9d4ceda3df","tid":650541,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"錢真係咁重要？<br />\n車？樓？<br />\n依家d人真係咁現實？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:27:54.000Z","msg":"唔現實就假<br />\n我可以同你一齊儲首期，但結婚一定要有樓搬出黎住<br />\n車好少事，二手都係幾萬蚊<br />\n我唔介意你窮，但介意你花費起無謂嘢上面"},"citedBy"